Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.db

Annotation Type DatabaseEngine.Innocuous

@Deprecated
@Documented
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public static @interface DatabaseEngine.Innocuous
Deprecated.
Consult the SQLite documentation on innocuous functions very carefully before enabling this. Only disable the deprecation warning if you're sure the security concerns it talks about have been accounted for.
If placed on a bean of type Function, specifies that the function may be used in schema structures. The DatabaseEngine assumes that all functions that are not innocuous must be direct-only.
Author:
Donal Fellows
See Also:
SQLITE_DIRECTONLY, SQLITE_INNOCUOUS
